metadata.name: XOLO # 1
metadata.description: This Xolo represents the feel of strength, agility, and elegance, all of which is preserved in the appearance of the Xolo Dog. Let this Xolo be your guide on the journey with us to Mictlan, he will give you strenght and power for the challenges and tests that we envision and enjoy the value that we are creating to our community and to others. Proud members of the XoloDAO
